\end_inset

, and Appendix
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec: appendix allowed lasing modes"

\end_inset

.) Second, we develop a numerical solution technique for 
\emph on
far above
\emph default
 threshold in Sec.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sub:Forcing-the-degeneracy"

\end_inset

